    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3069360/extras/3f7722947f1d08e2f91bf97095bd2846.gif?t=1761858284\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3069360/extras/3f7722947f1d08e2f91bf97095bd2846.poster.avif?t=1761858284\" class=\"bb_img\" /></picture></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3069360/extras/7e2259d7a36026a70dbd487f8287ed7a.poster.avif?t=1761858284\" width=864 height=87 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3069360/extras/7e2259d7a36026a70dbd487f8287ed7a.webm?t=1761858284\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Old school cool:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Inspired by 80s &amp; 90s classic slasher horror movies. Your every move is stalked by an adaptive villain hunting you all...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3069360/extras/ccaf632c4fe07c0870432812a9b649a6.poster.avif?t=1761858284\" width=555 height=75 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3069360/extras/ccaf632c4fe07c0870432812a9b649a6.webm?t=1761858284\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Survive the mansion:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Interact with the other survivors and try your best to help them. Are they really friend or foe? Or just another person trying to survive?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3069360/extras/ef966631afed7c0aaf9fcce40052f02e.poster.avif?t=1761858284\" width=555 height=75 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3069360/extras/ef966631afed7c0aaf9fcce40052f02e.webm?t=1761858284\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Help them or help yourself:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Trade with the other survivors and try to find your way out of this micro sandbox horror experience. Or use them as a human shield. Your choice!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3069360/extras/2eada50dd0dea611ed9121afe463333e.avif?t=1761858284\" width=810 height=75 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Creepy and gory:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Featuring unsettling top down pixel art aesthetics and tense atmosphere. Closely following rules of slasher horror movies in video game form for the connoisseur of retro inspired indie horror.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3069360/extras/ccd05456f5bf19d80559001b0b33c85d.avif?t=1761858284\" width=810 height=75 /></span> </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Micro sandbox.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Npc companions.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Randomised elements.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >An unpredictable villain.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Perma-death for you and your allies.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A bloody horrifying solo experience.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3069360/extras/a147e4f4010583fef16f42095fcefcca.poster.avif?t=1761858284\" width=705 height=99 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3069360/extras/a147e4f4010583fef16f42095fcefcca.webm?t=1761858284\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"></p>",
